# Lab 04 – Web Shell Upload Investigation

## Objective
Investigate a suspected web shell upload using Wireshark and analyze the HTTP traffic generated during the upload attempt.

## Skills Learned
- HTTP POST analysis
- File upload investigation
- HTTP status code analysis
- IOC collection
- SOC Tier-1 investigation

## Tools
- Kali Linux
- Ubuntu Server
- DVWA
- Wireshark

## Files
- report.md
- Lab04_WebShell_Upload.pcapng
- screenshots/

## MITRE ATT&CK
- T1505.003 – Web Shell

## Outcome
Successfully investigated a simulated web shell upload attempt, identified HTTP POST requests, verified the server response, collected IOCs, and documented findings.
